"thf(leibnitz_nontrivial_extensional,conjecture,
![F : $i>$i, G : $i>$i]:
  (![X : $i]: (
    (leibnitz_eq_i @ (F @ X) @ (G @ X))
    =>
    (leibnitz_eq_OPENiTOiCLOSE @ F @ G)
  ))
).")

run_prover(problem)
```

```elixir
