Example 21

```elixir
"
(
  (p @ ^[X : $o]: X) &
  (p @ ^[X : $o]: ~X) &
  (p @ ^[X : $o]: $false) &
  (p @ ^[X : $o]: $true)
)
=>
![Y : $o>$o]: p @ Y
" |> parse |> prove
```
